            "text": "And one head shall not be higher than another, and kings "
                    "shall not deny the Lord of Spirits; they shall bless and "
                    "glorify and extol the name of the Lord of Spirits.",
            "translation": "Charles"
        },

        "hebrew_terms": [],
        "ane_backdrop": None,
