                        "(2) ENTHRONEMENT: sits on the 'throne of glory' (62:5, "
                        "69:27). In Daniel, only the Ancient of Days is seated. "
                        "(3) JUDGMENT: actively judges kings and the mighty (62:1-12). "
                        "In Daniel, judgment belongs to the court/Ancient of Days. "
