                        "of Man with the Davidic Messiah (1 En 52:4; the Gospels). "
                        "Both describe kings falling before the Son of Man (1 En "
                        "62:9-10; Phil 2:10-11). The overlap is too extensive to be "
                        "coincidental, yet too diffuse to prove direct literary "
